WEBVTT

00:04.350 --> 00:06.413
Harry!
Thank God you called.

00:06.413 --> 00:08.663
Kate, where are you now?

00:08.663 --> 00:10.719
Oh, I'm on the way.

00:10.719 --> 00:12.749
I'll be there in 20 minutes.
How is she?

00:12.749 --> 00:13.672
I don't know.

00:13.672 --> 00:15.598
The veterinarian won't let me see her.

00:15.598 --> 00:16.898
Well, what did they say?

00:16.898 --> 00:19.220
She was hit by a car.
That's all they know.

00:19.220 --> 00:21.808
Oh! Oh, God.

00:22.504 --> 00:24.427
They think her back legs are broken.

00:24.427 --> 00:26.398
My poor baby.

00:26.702 --> 00:29.510
I don't know how it happened.
How did she get out of the yard?

00:29.510 --> 00:32.118
Maria must have left the gate open.

00:32.118 --> 00:34.267
I don't think so.
I checked it myself.

00:34.267 --> 00:35.469
Where are you now?

00:35.469 --> 00:38.955
Oh, I'm, uh...
I'm going past the ranger station.

00:39.274 --> 00:42.003
Oh, God, if something's happened to her,
I will never forgive myself.

00:42.003 --> 00:43.583
Just hurry!

00:44.085 --> 00:46.766
I'm... I'm going as fast as I can.

